<abstract><t>In this draft, we provide architecture and operations for enabling IP services over ICN over (5G-enabled) LAN environments.  Operations include ICN API to upper layers, HTTP over ICN, Service Proxy Operations, ICN Flow Management, Name Resolution, Mobility Handling, and Dual Stack Device Support.</t></abstract>

